<collectingCountry box="[1078,1117,1159,1185]" name="Fiji" pageId="7" pageNumber="508">Fiji</collectingCountry>
Bioinventory of Arthropods Study, Evert Irving Schlinger (1928–2014), an entomologist, a recognized expert on spider-parasitoid flies of the family 
<taxonomicName box="[230,371,1231,1257]" class="Insecta" family="Acroceridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="508" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Acroceridae</taxonomicName>
